text: John Porch (born 4 March 1994) is an Australian professional rugby union player, currently playing for Irish side Connacht. Porch will join Irish province Connacht, who compete in the Pro14 and European Rugby Champions Cup, ahead of the 2019–20 northern hemisphere season. Connacht's current head coach is former Australia 7s head coach Andy Friend. ==Australia== He represented Australia at the 2016 Rio Olympics.
